  "texts": [
    "The GPT-2 model used here is gpt2 (small), with 124M parameters.",
    "train is stratify-sampled by the class to ensure every class is represented, and to reduce the variance of accuracy estimators.",
    "test is not stratifysampled.",
    "We are only interested in the difference between accuracies, which is a function of the difference between model likelihoods because the priors are uniform.",
    "So even if accuracies are worse than the majority vote, differences are still meaningful for the purposes of this experiment."
  ],
